# Objective: BYON

A service that implements the Bring Your Own Notebook (BYON) MVP in the context of Open Data Hub (ODH). The MVP is targeted to complete by **Red Hat Summit (May 2022)** and some of the work is still ongoing.

## KRs Defined

To accomplish the objective, the following Key Results (KRs) have been defined:

* **Validation pipeline implemented for container images input**. The issues/PRs that need to be completed to achieve the KR are:
  * https://github.com/thoth-station/helm-charts/pull/34
  * https://github.com/open-services-group/byon/issues/26
  * https://github.com/thoth-station/helm-charts/pull/35
  * https://github.com/open-services-group/byon/issues/30
  * https://github.com/open-services-group/byon/issues/18

* **UI mockup design for the admin interface to import, edit, enable/disable, remove container images (admin feature)** The issues/PRs that need to be completed to achieve the KR are:
  * https://github.com/open-services-group/byon/issues/23
* **Frontend and Backend Implementation**. The issues/PRs that need to be completed to achieve the KR are:
  * https://github.com/opendatahub-io/odh-dashboard/issues/121
  * https://github.com/opendatahub-io/odh-dashboard/pull/147
  * https://github.com/opendatahub-io/odh-dashboard/pull/155
  * https://github.com/opendatahub-io/odh-dashboard/pull/156

* **Integrating backend and UI**. The issues/PRs that need to be completed to achieve the KR are:
  * https://github.com/opendatahub-io/odh-dashboard/issues/121
  
* **Testing** The issues/PRs that need to be completed to achieve the KR are:
  * https://github.com/open-services-group/byon/issues/34
  * https://github.com/open-services-group/byon/pull/29
